{"tid":617514,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人深度遊過保加利亞🇧🇬？","createTime":"2018-04-05T04:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T23:31:32.000Z","uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8d4b092953266d6ff4917a2c32b4b7c96c45fc","tid":617514,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:42:05.000Z","msg":"作為歐盟入最窮嘅國家之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歐洲人同亞洲人對呢個國家反應都幾兩極，可能價值唔同？<br />\n東方人講起都係話首都好悶冇咩景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾盡大陸二線城市質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者唯一印象得Hea碧托夫<br />\n=保加利亞人都係hea/粗魯<br />\n<br />\n身邊啲歐洲朋友，就會講起拜占庭嘅歷史，又或者係巴爾幹戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對歷史冇咁有興趣嘅，都會話識一兩個做緊地盤嘅移民(主要英國)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而低廉嘅物價同東邊接壤黑海嘅海岸線<br />\n使佢成為西意之後一個熱門嘅getaways <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲去過分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032c53216b496a8977a2d4c3ef84c2bb2a7fc41d","tid":617514,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:43:06.000Z","msg":"當然仲有賣妻嗰啲癡線嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔講住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f834178c1196ab651ad5d24727f50cf26f2fd27c","tid":617514,"uid":57854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"想去但未去過 留名先"},{"pid":"25c3b5bbbad7f6c3e14831c82321b8eea30435a4","tid":617514,"uid":136901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:45:33.000Z","msg":"貝碧<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ce8afe5fc28e4e154df5ccbe6169fd30d81cd6","tid":617514,"uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:50:29.000Z","msg":"留名，八月去，仲想couchsurfing 會唔會太危險？"},{"pid":"5966bd9cf03f02714a646d7b39ba13463e0dd86a","tid":617514,"uid":53911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:59:16.000Z","msg":"淺度遊過Sofia同Plovdiv , 再跟團去rila monastery <br />\n其實sofia都幾正 物價低 咩國家嘅野食都有，我走左去食印度咖哩同壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，睇多左西歐教堂睇下東正教建築個感覺好唔同，街上極少出現亞洲面孔，試過係街比兩個後生local撩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地推介我去黑海嗰邊玩，不過d人英文認真麻麻地"},{"pid":"de32312c3ec04ac492cb56e6abf262c967d238d2","tid":617514,"uid":93776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:04:23.000Z","msg":"跟host 去過Buzludzha<br />\n可能我對廢墟比較有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a1d7e247008546fa11ffe9149b4e84bea355b2","tid":617514,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de32312c3ec04ac492cb56e6abf262c967d238d2","tid":617514,"uid":93776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:04:23.000Z","msg":"跟host 去過Buzludzha<br />\n可能我對廢墟比較有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"個host車埋你去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f755cfc2eff7425d17bcc98ebe08d5272748cb66","tid":617514,"uid":60550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"好鍾意Veliko Tarnovo<br />\n我個時都係度出發去Buzludzha 係hostel好難得地搵到人夾份租車去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a427da7eb8b473dd3488e59e2f3dbe92003b5f","tid":617514,"uid":96107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"去保加利亞唔去七湖（行去里拉修道院）同皮林國家公園=無去"},{"pid":"14888b7051113b9eaef12eb3ebff41789c7ba797","tid":617514,"uid":1279,"like":0,"dislike":0,